criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Work shift continuity in a specific group of at least one year.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Presence of cardiovascular, endocrine or metabolic diseases;

          -  Presence of neurological or musculoskeletal impairments at finger flexors muscles
             level;

          -  Pharmacological therapies in place that can affect the heart rate and the sleep
             quality;

          -  Self-declaration of pregnancy.
